Q25: The TeamingxDesign team is developing machine learning algorithms to process the responses provided in these teaming assessments. We aim to make these assessment and feedback processes increasingly helpful to your learning experience. We may share our findings in academic research papers to help other educators teach teaming. Before we analyze the data, we remove all identifying information, including your name and email, as well as the name of the class. We ask your consent to add your anonymized responses to the growing dataset of teaming data. Your choice to participate in the research or not WILL NOT AFFECT  your ability to finish class assignments, receive feedback from these assessments, or your grade in the class. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact Sara Beckman (beckman@berkeley.edu).
